__version 1.0__

* Possibility for providing recipient list as command line argument
* Load a default config file in users home  ~/.sendxmpp++
* Define configuration order: (cmdline) overrides (-c config) overrides (~/.config)
* Add error checking, more verbose stderr.cout
* Add source code comments

__version 1.1__

* Add sanity check for input
* Add support for crypted passwords


